{"word":"συγκαθίζω","slug":"συγκαθίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συγκαθίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ιζήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make to sit together</i>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> or <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to sit in conclave, meet for deliberation</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a>, = <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to sit with</i> one, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}